  "description": {
    "main": "Savour your music wherever you are with the Sony WH-1000XM6. The QN3 Processor is in charge of cancelling noise around you, so you can get lost in the sound of your music, podcast, or a TV show. Thanks to 30 mm drivers and 360 Upmix for Cinema, everything will sound its best – with rumbly lows, clear vocals and bright highs. The Auto NC Optimiser automatically adjusts the sound profile to your environment, so you'll always get the most out of your music. Switch between your iPhone and Android, or PC and Mac with multipoint Bluetooth connection that lets you connect two devices at the same time.",
    "goodToKnow": [
      "The six microphones use AI noise reduction to make your voice sound clear on calls – even in a busy office",
      "It's for more than just music - Game EQ makes it great for getting your game on too",
      "With up to 30 hours of battery life, you'll have enough juice for days of listening",
      "Thanks to quick charging, just three minutes on the charger will give you up to one hour of play time",
      "The earcup controls let you control your music, incoming calls, or summon your smart assistant",
      "The included magnetic closure carry case will keep your headphones safe and sound, even in a stuffed backpack"
